      <title>中国人民银行通过定盘汇率为人民币提供自 11 月份以来最强劲的提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/pboc-provides-strongest-boost-to-yuan-via-fixing-since-november</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行将受管理货币的每日参考汇率设定为去年 11 月以来的最大差距，以遏制人民币疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/pboc-provides-strongest-boost-to-yuan-via-fixing-since-november</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 01:19:30 GMT</pubDate>
