    <item>
      <title>摩根大通资产称美联储降息幅度可能比预期更大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/jpmorgan-asset-says-fed-rate-cuts-may-be-steeper-than-expected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产管理公司表示，随着美国经济放缓，美联储最终的降息幅度可能会超过目前的信号，从而推动短期国债上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/jpmorgan-asset-says-fed-rate-cuts-may-be-steeper-than-expected</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:19:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的宽客将遭受自动化商品交易退款削减的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/quants-in-china-to-suffer-from-cuts-to-automated-commodity-trading-refunds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国大宗商品交易所正在终止某些自动化交易的退款，因为当局试图减少市场波动，从而帮助确定该国购买原材料的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/quants-in-china-to-suffer-from-cuts-to-automated-commodity-trading-refunds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:14:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>住宅建筑商在 2024 年首次引人注目的美国 IPO 中筹集了 1.62 亿美元，超额完成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/homebuilder-raises-162-million-at-top-of-range-in-first-notable-us-ipo-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，史密斯道格拉斯住宅公司 (Smith Douglas Homes Corp.) 在首次公开募股中将股票定价为市场区间的最高价，筹集了约 1.62 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/homebuilder-raises-162-million-at-top-of-range-in-first-notable-us-ipo-of-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:04:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
